%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/T%C3%A0n-xu%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-lai-nam-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-nh%C3%A2n-k%C3%BD-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/poem-ApML1iv9tc-rJd1cozF7pg">Tàn xuân độc lai nam đình nhân ký Trương Hỗ - 殘春獨來南亭因寄張祜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%C3%B4-t%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%81/poem-bR8QGem88oZhdNps2IvS6Q">Tặng Tô tứ Hề - 贈蘇四徯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/Th%C3%A1i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%E1%BB%A5c-duy-%C4%91%C3%AA/poem-6d7KgNUN_5XafANLFYq-og">Thái phụng trục duy đê - 彩鳳逐帷低</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
